Important Commands
_______________________________

To create an interactive job on the cluster and work on jupyter:

srun --pty -t 1-0 --partition=mundus --gres=gpu:a100-20 bash

jupyter notebook --port 30333

then if we want to work from the local machine: ssh -L 30333:localhost:30333 <<cluster-login-node>> ssh -L 30333:localhost:30333 <<cluster-compute-node>>

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

using screen: 

nvidia-smi

screen
run interactive job
detach: ctrl a d
reattach: screen -R 
close screen: ctrl d 
